node.title: Diver dies at Goat Island after water incident
node.description: Police say a group of three divers got into difficulty.
node.content: ["One person is dead at Goat Island, north of Auckland, on Saturday.", "Police say emergency services were alerted to a group of three divers in difficulty in the water at around 1:35pm.\u00a0", "\"CPR was performed one of the divers but sadly they died at the scene,\" a spokesperson says.", "\"The two other divers were uninjured.\"", "Enquiries are ongoing to determine the circumstances of the incident."]
